# VTMotionBlurParameters.SubmissionMode.sequential

**Case**

A submission follow presentation time order without a jump or skip when compared to a previous submission.

## Declaration

```swift
case sequential
```

## Discussion

This submission mode will yield a better performance.

## Submission modes

- **VTMotionBlurParameters.SubmissionMode.random**: A submission follow presentation time order with a jump or skip in a frame sequence.
